{{noteTA
|G1=EL
|G2=P
|G3=Communication
}}
{{amateur radio}}
[[File:Amateurfunkstation.jpg|thumb]]

'''业余无线电'''（{{lang-en|'''Amateur Radio'''}}），也被称作'''火腿电台'''（{{lang-en|'''ham radio'''}}）是一种供业余无线电爱好者进行相互通信、[[无线通讯|无线通讯]]技术实验、自我训练、个人娱乐、{{tsl|en|Radiosport|无线电运动}}、{{tsl|en|Contesting|竞赛 (业余无线电)|竞赛}}以及[[业余无线电应急通信|应急通信]]的一项使用[[无线电频率|无线电频率]][[无线电频谱|频谱]]的无线电业务。其中“业余无线电爱好者”指“经正式批准的、对无线电技术有兴趣的人，其兴趣纯系个人爱好而不涉及谋取利润”{{noteTag|1= 此处“业余”并非指参与者水平低，而是指他们只将其作为业余爱好。}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/dms_pub/itu-s/oth/02/02/S02020000204501PDFE.pdf |title=General Regulations Annexed to the International Radiotelegraph Convention |work=International Radiotelegraph Convention of Washington, 1927 |publisher=His Majesty's Stationery Office |location=London |pages=29-172 |date=1928 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728130153/https://www.itu.int/dms_pub/itu-s/oth/02/02/S02020000204501PDFE.pdf |archivedate=2017-07-28 |access-date=2017-07-07 }}</ref>。业余无线电与[[商业广播|商业广播]]、安全业务无线电{{noteTag|1=例如警用与消防用无线电。}}或者其他专业{{tsl|en|Two-way radio|双向无线电}}业务{{noteTag|1=例如船用、航空和公众对讲机无线电。}}存在区别，业余无线电并非这些专业无线电业务的业余形式，也不是有关这些业务的业余爱好，而是一项独立的无线电业务。

'''业余无线电业务'''（包括业余业务和{{tsl|en|Amateur-satellite service|卫星业余业务}}）由[[国际电信联盟|国际电信联盟]]（ITU）通过《{{tsl|en|Radio Regulations|无线电规则}}》设立<ref name="RR">{{Cite book |url=http://handle.itu.int/11.1002/pub/80da2b36-en |last=国际电信联盟   |date=2016 |publisher=国际电信联盟 |isbn=9789261177959 |edition=2016年版 |location=日内瓦 |title=无线电规则 |access-date=2017-10-03 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121803/http://www.itu.int/pub/R-REG-RR-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|at=1.56}}。在国家层面上，政府对业余无线电业务进行管理，并为每一个独立的业余电台指配[[业余无线电呼号|呼号]] 。“准”业余无线电爱好者需要接受考试，以检测其对无线电技术和所在国无线电法规的掌握。

业余无线电爱好者使用语音、文字、图像和数据等形式，借助[[无线电波|无线电波]]，跨越城市、国家和大洲的距离相互通信，甚至与空间站和卫星建立通信链路。

在国际上，业余无线电业务由[[国际业余无线电联盟|国际业余无线电联盟]]（IARU）代表和协调，国际业余无线电联盟由全国性业余无线电协会{{noteTag|大多数国家都存在全国性业余无线电协会。}}组成<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iaru.org/about.html |title=About - International Amateur Radio Union |accessdate=2017-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815135112/http://www.iaru.org/about.html |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。

根据2011年{{tsl|en|American Radio Relay League|美国无线电中继联盟}}（ARRL）的统计，全球共有约200万人参与业余无线电活动<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Sumner |first1=David |title=How Many Hams? |magazine=QST |date=August 2011 |page=9 |publisher=American Radio Relay League}}</ref>。其中约有83万{{tsl|en|amateur radio station|业余业务电台}}位于IARU区域2（美洲），约75万位于IARU区域3（亚太地区），约40万位于IARU区域1（欧洲、中东、独联体国家和非洲）。

==历史==
{{Main article|{{tsl|en|History of amateur radio|业余无线电历史}}}}
[[File:mw0rkbshack.jpg|thumb]]
<!--Please do not add extensive info to this section; instead, go to the "History of amateur radio" page-->
业余无线电的诞生可以追溯到19世纪末，但现代意义上的业余无线电活动起始于20世纪初。出版于1909年的《美国无线协会第一版年度官方无线蓝皮书》（{{lang-en|''First Annual Official Wireless Blue Book of the Wireless Association of America''}}）包含了一份业余无线电台的列表。<ref name="bluebook1909">{{cite book |url=http://www.seas.upenn.edu/~uparc/documents/First%20Annual%20Official%20Wireless%20Blue%20Book%20-%201909.pdf |format=PDF |title=First Annual Official Wireless Blue Book of the Wireless Association of America |publisher=Modern Electrics Publication |location=[[New_York_City|New York]] |first=H |last=Gernsback |date=May 1909 |accessdate=2009-06-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706002250/http://www.seas.upenn.edu/~uparc/documents/First%20Annual%20Official%20Wireless%20Blue%20Book%20-%201909.pdf |archivedate=2010-07-06 }}</ref>这份{{tsl|en|Broadcast_call_signs#Callbooks|呼号手册}}列举了加拿大和美国的[[无线电报|无线电报]]电台，包括89个业余电台。与其他无线电业务一样，业余无线电也与各种业余实验和爱好相关。业余无线电爱好者在[[科学|科学]]、[[工程学|工程]]、[[工业|工业]]和[[社会服务|社会服务]]领域做出了巨大贡献。由业余无线电操作员进行的研究建立了新的[[产业|产业]]<ref>{{cite conference |url=http://www.bliley.net/XTAL/Industry-Hams.html |title=The Influence of Amateur Radio on the Development of the Commercial Market for Quartz Piezoelectric Resonators in the United States |conference=1996 IEEE International Frequency Control Symposium. 5-7 June 1996. Honolulu, Hawaii. |first=Patrick R. J. |last=Brown |date=1996 |doi=10.1109/FREQ.1996.559819 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113003917/http://www.bliley.net/XTAL/Industry-Hams.html |archivedate=2013-01-13 |access-date=2010-12-11 }}</ref>，促进了经济发展<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2000/kilby-autobio.html |title=Inventor of IC 'chip', Nobel Prize Winner Jack S. Kilby Credits Amateur Radio for His Start in Electronics |publisher=Nobelprize.org |date=2005-06-20 |accessdate=2012-11-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105132023/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2000/kilby-autobio.html |archivedate=2012-11-05 }}</ref>，提升了国家实力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cimap.vt.edu/files/internet/Impression/ICT.pdf |title=''Role of Amateur Radio in Development Communication of Bangladesh.'' Information & Communication Technology for Development. By Bazlur Rahman |accessdate=2017-07-07 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092904/http://www.cimap.vt.edu/files/internet/Impression/ICT.pdf |dead-url=yes }}{{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092904/http://www.cimap.vt.edu/files/internet/Impression/ICT.pdf |date=2015-05-18 }}</ref>，并且多次在紧急情况下拯救了生命<ref>{{cite web |author=Jim Taylor |url=http://www.hfradio.net/bulletin/jan0205i.html |title=Canadian Amateur Radio Bulletin, ''Amateur Radio "Saved Lives" in South Asia'' (2004-12-29) |publisher=Hfradio.net |date= |accessdate=2012-11-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306182700/http://www.hfradio.net/bulletin/jan0205i.html |archivedate=2012-03-06 }}</ref><ref name="ARRL-whatis">{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/what-is-ham-radio |title=What is Ham Radio? |work=ARRL.org |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100504001349/http://www.arrl.org/what-is-ham-radio-1 |archivedate=2010-05-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。业余无线电也在课堂中被用于教授英语、地图阅读技巧、地理知识、数学、科学和计算机技术<ref>{{cite journal |title=On the Air Learning |journal=Teaching Pre K-8 |first=Bruce D. |last=Weaver |volume=33 |issue=4 |pages=50–51 |date=January 2003 |issn=0891-4508}}</ref>。

===火腿电台===
{{main article|{{tsl|en|Etymology of ham radio|火腿电台的词源}}}}
“火腿”一词最早是作为19世纪专业有线电报操作员嘲笑“报务技术较差的操作员”（{{lang-en|[[wiktionary:ham-fisted|'''ham'''-fisted]]}}）的[[贬义|贬义]]词<ref>"Ham Fisted", ''QST'', August 1972, p83.</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Tales of the telegraph |last=Brady |first=Jasper Ewing |year=1899 |url=https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=6BgZAAAAYAAJ&hl=en |accessdate=2013-02-01 |publisher=Doubleday & McClure Co. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309090101/https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=6BgZAAAAYAAJ&hl=en |archivedate=2014-03-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-history |title=Ham Radio History |publisher=Arrl.org |date= |accessdate=2015-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510223641/http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-history |archivedate=2015-05-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://earlyradiohistory.us/1902slng.htm |title=Telegraph Talk and Talkers-slang extract (1902) |publisher=Earlyradiohistory.us |date= |accessdate=2015-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518082637/http://earlyradiohistory.us/1902slng.htm |archivedate=2015-05-18 }}</ref>。无线电技术发明后，有关无线电报的业余无线电实验激增，这一情况使专业无线电操作员对“火腿”电台操作员十分讨厌，因而对他们也使用了“火腿”一词。业余无线电社群随后开始将“火腿”一词视作荣耀的象征<ref>{{cite web |url=http://earlyradiohistory.us/1920pome.htm |title=I am the Wandering Ham "pome" (1920) |publisher=Earlyradiohistory.us |date= |accessdate=2015-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518082638/http://earlyradiohistory.us/1920pome.htm |archivedate=2015-05-18 }}</ref>，随后在20世纪中叶，“火腿”一词已经没有了原来的贬义。“火腿”一词的“业余或水平低下”的词义（{{lang-en|"ham actor"}}）在其他学科仍沿用至今。<ref name="dict_ham">{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/990045353 |title=牛津高阶英汉双解词典 |last=Turnbull |first=Joanna |last2=Lea |first2=Diana |last3=Parkinson |first3=Dilys |last4=Phillips |first4=Patrick |last5=Ashby |first5=Michael |last6=陆 |first6=谷孙 |last7=石 |first7=孝殊 |last8=赵 |first8=翠莲 |last9=邹 |first9=晓玲 |date=2015-06 |publisher=商务印书馆 |year=2015 |isbn=9787100110969 |edition=第八版 |location=北京 |pages=946 |chapter=ham |oclc=990045353 |access-date=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121759/https://www.worldcat.org/title/niujin-gao-jie-ying-han-shuang-jie-ci-dian-di-ba-ban-oxford-advanced-learners-english-chinese-dictionary-eighth-edition/oclc/990045353 |dead-url=no }}</ref>虽然“火腿”（{{lang-en|ham}}）并非一个缩合词<ref name="dict_ham" />，有时其也被误拼写为全大写的“HAM”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://w1af.harvard.edu/hamorigin.html |title=Origin of the Term 'HAM' |publisher=Harvard Wireless Club |date=1999 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527172642/http://w1af.harvard.edu/hamorigin.html |archivedate=2009-05-27 |accessdate=2018-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mc.harvard.edu/w1af/members/w1afarticle.html |title=A Collegiate Radio Milestone |publisher=Harvard Wireless Club |first=Mike |last=Manafo |date=1999 |accessdate=2015-04-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060911220039/http://mc.harvard.edu/w1af/members/w1afarticle.html |archivedate=2006-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.qsl.net/sars/the_origin_of_the_word_ham.htm |title=Why Radio Amateurs Are Called 'HAMs' |work=Florida Skip Magazine |publisher=QSL.net |date=1959 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810072400/http://www.qsl.net/sars/the_origin_of_the_word_ham.htm |archivedate=2011-08-10 |accessdate=2018-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在中文环境中，'''火腿族'''为通过业余无线电考试的爱好者，至於'''香肠族'''则为中华地区创出的名词，指的是尚未通过业余无线电考试、正在学习的无线电玩家<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://market.cloud.edu.tw/content/junior/scouting/tc_jr/304/sourcemain.htm|title=01教學資源~~主目錄|accessdate=2018-05-12|work=market.cloud.edu.tw|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180513081740/https://market.cloud.edu.tw/content/junior/scouting/tc_jr/304/sourcemain.htm|archivedate=2018-05-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/862640624 |title=业余无线电通信：“香肠族”读本 |last=李 |first=娅君 |date=2010-05-01 |publisher=北京理工大学出版社 |year=2010 |isbn=9787564031640 |location=北京 |language=zh-cn |oclc=862640624 |access-date=2018-05-31 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121759/https://www.worldcat.org/title/ye-yu-wu-xian-dian-tong-xin/oclc/862640624 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==活动==

业余无线电丰富的活动吸引了大量的爱好者。许多爱好者从无线电通联{{noteTag|爱好者们把业余无线电台之间相互通信的活动称作通联。}}开始了这项爱好，并将这项爱好与其他个人兴趣结合起来，追求个人的快乐<ref name="whatdohamsdo"/>。业余无线电爱好者热衷的重点领域包括{{tsl|en|contesting|竞赛（业余无线电）|无线电竞赛}}、{{tsl|en|Radio propagation|无线电传播}}研究、{{tsl|en|Amateur radio homebrew|自制（业余无线电）|技术试验}}以及[[业余无线电应急通信|应急通信]]<ref name="whatdohamsdo">{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/883414262 |last=Ward |first=Silver, H. |last2=Debra |first2=Johnson |publisher=American Radio Relay League |year=2016 |isbn=9781625950130 |edition=Third edition |location=Newington, CT |pages=1-8 |chapter=What do hams do? |oclc=883414262 |title=The ARRL Ham Radio License Manual |access-date=2018-08-20 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121807/https://www.worldcat.org/title/arrl-ham-radio-license-manual-all-you-need-to-become-an-amateur-radio-operator/oclc/883414262 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===通联===
业余无线电操作员使用他们的业余电台，利用空中的电波与其他爱好者通联。通联的内容多种多样，爱好者们可以只交换必要的信息，也可以讨论技术，通联甚至可以仅仅是一场“火腿神聊”{{noteTag|即闲聊。}}（{{lang-en|rag chew sessions}}）。但是，业余电台禁止从事商业或其他与盈利有关的活动，业余无线电爱好者也应当避免在通联中谈论政治和宗教等容易引发争论的话题<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nuttycellist-unknown.blogspot.com/2011/09/old-question-contest-or-ragchew.html |title=The old question, contest or ragchew? |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=Shin Onisawa |date=2011-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815175356/http://nuttycellist-unknown.blogspot.com/2011/09/old-question-contest-or-ragchew.html |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref><ref name="protocol"/>。

一些爱好者也参加定期举行的、被称为“{{tsl|en|Amateur radio net|业余无线电台网|台网}}”的“空中”聚会，台网由其中以为被称作“台网主控”的电台主持<ref name="netcontrol">{{cite web |url=http://www.scc-ares-races.org/mtnview/principles-of-net-control.html |title=Principles of Amateur Radio Net Control |work=SCC-AREA-RACES.org |first=Jerry |last=Haag |accessdate=2007-01-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060507132245/http://www.scc-ares-races.org/mtnview/principles-of-net-control.html |archivedate=2006-05-07 }}</ref>。台网为爱好者们提供了学习应急通信程序、组成讨论小组、交流爱好的机会<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mide.io/blog/2015/10/19/running-a-ham-radio-net.html |title=RUNNING A HAM RADIO NET |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=Mark Ide Jr |date=2015-10-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815175447/https://www.mide.io/blog/2015/10/19/running-a-ham-radio-net.html |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。

====通联程序====
{|style="margin: auto"
!语音模式（汉语）
!语音模式（英语）
!电报或数字模式
|--
|width=1000 style="border: 1px solid #F0ABB2; background: #FFEBEC; padding:20px"|
CQ{{NoteTag|在业余无线电术语中表示广泛呼叫。}} CQ CQ， 这里是BI8CKU，Bravo India Eight Charlie Kilo Uniform{{NoteTag|这位业余无线电爱好者使用[[字母解释法|字母解释法]]重复自己的呼号，以确保其他爱好者能够正确抄收呼号。}}，BI8CKU呼叫CQ，等待应答。<br>
----
BI8CKU，这里是BI8DJW，Bravo India Eight Delta Juliet Whiskey，BI8DJW呼叫。<br>
----
BI8DJW，这里是BI8CKU，您的信号是59{{NoteTag|对方的[[信号报告|信号报告]]。}}，我的信号怎么样？完毕。<br>
----
BI8CKU，这里是BI8DJW，您的信号也是59。完毕。<br>
----
BI8DJW，很高兴与您通联。73{{NoteTag|在业余无线电术语中表示美好的祝福。<ref name="ham-radio-glossary"/>}}，再见。这里是BI8CKU，结束通联。<br>
----
BI8CKU，这里是BI8DJW，73，再见。<br>
|width=1000 style="border: 1px solid #FFEA71; background: #FFF9D1; padding:20px"|
CQ CQ CQ, this is BI8CKU, Bravo India Eight Charlie Kilo Uniform, BI8CKU calling CQ and standing by.<br>
----
BI8CKU, this is BI8DJW, Bravo India Eight Delta Juliet Whiskey, BI8DJW calling.<br>
----
BI8DJW, this is BI8CKU, your signal is 59. How is my signal? Over.<br>
----
BI8CKU, this is BI8DJW, your signal is 59, too. Over.<br>
----
BI8DJW,  thank you for the contact, 73 and bye-bye. This is BI8CKU, signing off.<br>
----
BI8CKU, this is BI8DJW, 73 and bye-bye.<br>
|width=1000 style="border: 1px solid #CEF2E0; background: #F5FFFA; padding:20px"|
CQ CQ CQ DE BI8CKU BI8CKU BI8CKU K<br>
----
BI8CKU DE BI8DJW BI8DJW BI8DJW K<br>
----
BI8DJW UR RST 599 K<br>
----
BI8CKU UR RST 599 K<br>
----
BI8DJW TNX FER QSO 73 ES GB DE BI8CKU SK<br>
----
BI8CKU DE BI8DJW 73 ES GB SK<br>
|}
业余无线电通联遵循一定的格式和习惯。一次通联通常以一个电台在频率上呼叫CQ开始，CQ代表广泛呼叫<ref name="ham-radio-glossary">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-glossary |title=Ham Radio Glossary |accessdate=2018-07-16 |author=ARRL |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716170216/http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-glossary |archivedate=2018-07-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，即呼叫此刻频率上的任何电台；紧接着，有兴趣通联的另一个电台回复并报出自己的呼号，在双方都抄收对方呼号后，双方需要交换[[信号报告|信号报告]]，交换完毕后，一次通联即告成功，此时双方可以继续就感兴趣的话题深入交流，或直接互相告别结束通联；在通联结束后，双方必须将此次通联的关键信息{{NoteTag|至少应当记录[[UTC|UTC]]日期时间、对方呼号、通信频率、通信模式、双方的信号报告。}}记入电台日志，许多爱好者也会互相交换[[QSL卡|QSL卡片]]<ref name="protocol">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/files/file/DXCC/Eth-operating-EN-ARRL-CORR-JAN-2011.pdf |title=Ethics and Operating Procedures for the Radio Amateur |accessdate=2018-07-16 |author=John Devoldere |coauthors=Mark Demeuleneere, Bob Whelan |date=2011-06 |publisher=International Amateur Radio Union |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610231604/http://www.arrl.org/files/file/DXCC/Eth-operating-EN-ARRL-CORR-JAN-2011.pdf |archivedate=2017-06-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/making-your-first-contact |title=Making Your First Contact |accessdate=2018-07-16 |author=ARRL |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716170100/http://www.arrl.org/making-your-first-contact |archivedate=2018-07-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===中继台===
为了提升通信范围，业余无线电爱好者也架设{{tsl|en|Amateur radio repeater|业余无线电中继台|中继台}}。这些中继台通常位于地势较高处，能够转发和放大手持机和移动[[收发信机|收发信机]]的信号，从而能使得[[VHF|VHF]]以及更高频率的信号覆盖更广的范围<ref name="fsat">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.arrl.org/tis/info/pdf/49319.pdf |format=PDF |title=An Introduction to Amateur Television |magazine={{tsl|en|QST|QST杂志|QST}} ''via'' ARRL.org |first=Ralph E |last=Taggart |date=April 1993 |pages=19–23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070605111732/http://www.arrl.org/tis/info/pdf/49319.pdf |archivedate=2007-06-05 |access-date=2017-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。中继台也能通过其他[[业余无线电频率划分|频点]]、有线链路或{{tsl|en|Internet Radio Linking Project|互联网电台连接计划|互联网}}组成网络，从而提供更广的通信范围<ref>{{cite web |last=Valdes |first=Robert |url=http://communication.howstuffworks.com/ip-telephony10.htm |title=HowStuffWorks: Use of VoIP in Amateur Radio |publisher=Communication.howstuffworks.com |date=2001-05-09 |accessdate=2012-11-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114173645/http://communication.howstuffworks.com/ip-telephony10.htm |archivedate=2012-01-14 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.irlp.net/ |title=IRLP The Internet Radio Linking Project |accessdate=2017-08-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916155221/http://irlp.net/ |archivedate=2017-09-16 }}</ref>。

===空间通信===
[[File:ISS-24_Doug_Wheelock_uses_ham_radio_system_1.jpg|thumb]]的[[星辰号服务舱|星辰号服务舱]]，设备为[[建伍|建伍]]TM-D700E收发信机。]]

1961年12月12日，业余无线电爱好者将第一颗{{tsl|en|Amateur radio satellite|业余无线电卫星}}“奥斯卡1号”（{{lang-en|OSCAR-1, '''O'''rbiting '''S'''atellite '''C'''arrying '''A'''mateur '''R'''adio}}）送上了太空，这标志了业余无线电进入了空间时代。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.amsat.org/amsat-new/AboutAmsat/amsat_history.php | title=Space Satellites from the World's Garage – The Story of AMSAT | publisher=AMSAT-NA | accessdate=2013-02-14 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061005160332/http://www.amsat.org/amsat-new/AboutAmsat/amsat_history.php | archivedate=2006-10-05 }}</ref>爱好者可以使用超短波收发信机和高增益定向天线与{{tsl|en|Amateur radio satellite|业余无线电卫星}}连线，通过卫星对信号的转发实现远距离通信<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amsat.org/amsat/intro/sats_faq.html |title=Amateur Satellite FAQ |last=Holmstead |first=Stephen |date=1994-12-30 |publisher=The Radio Amateur Satellite Corporation |accessdate=2010-03-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100106121014/http://www.amsat.org/amsat/intro/sats_faq.html |archivedate=2010-01-06 }}</ref>。

月球是地球的天然卫星，早在1940年就有工程师提出了利用月面反射无线电信号进行远距离通信的设想<ref>{{cite book| last = Pether  | first = John  | title = The Post Office at War | publisher = Bletchley Park Trust  | date = 1998  | page = 25 }}</ref>，但由于{{tsl|en|EME (communications)|月面反射通信}}（EME）极高的路径损耗和更有效的卫星通信技术的出现，EME一直没有得到实际运用。火腿族继承了这一未竟的事业，1953年，美国的两位爱好者成功进行了业余无线电第一次EME通信实验<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ok2kkw.com/eme1960/eme1960eng.htm |title=The first Amateur Lunar tests & contacts 1953-1965 |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=Czech VHF/UHF Ham Radio Contest Club |date=2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126213202/http://www.ok2kkw.com/eme1960/eme1960eng.htm |archivedate=2017-11-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。月面反射通信相较于卫星通信，需要电台和天线具有更高的灵敏度和增益，也要求爱好者拥有更高的技术，被视作为业余无线电超短波通信的巅峰<ref>{{Cite journal |title=月面反射通讯概览 |author=吴国光 |journal=电子制作 |publisher=中国家用电器服务维修协会 |issue=2014年5期 |year=2014 |page=16-23 |issn=1006-5059}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.lifewieller.com/2015/10/%E6%9C%88%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1-%E8%BF%9C%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95/ |title=月面反射通信——远比你想象的简单 |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=LifeWieller |date=2015-10-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709154344/https://www.lifewieller.com/2015/10/%E6%9C%88%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1-%E8%BF%9C%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95/ |archivedate=2018-07-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。火腿族也利用[[极光|极光]]以及[[流星|流星]]的电离尾迹反射无线电信号进行通联<ref name="WJST">{{cite news |url=http://www.arrl.org/tis/info/pdf/0112036.pdf |format=PDF |title=''WSJT'': New Software for VHF Meteor-Scatter Communication |work=QST ''via'' ARRL.org |first=Joe |last=Taylor |date=December 2001 |pages=36–41 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5n7b4aGqW?url=http://www.arrl.org/tis/info/pdf/0112036.pdf |archivedate=2010-01-28 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2017-07-07 }}</ref>。

1983年11月28日，呼号为W5LFL的宇航员[[欧文·加里欧特|欧文·加里欧特]]在[[STS-9|STS-9]]任务中使用手持式业余电台与地面成功通联，成为了在太空中操作业余电台的第一人，他的这一行动成功向NASA展示了业余无线电对于科普的积极作用，由此开启了{{tsl|en|Shuttle Amateur Radio Experiment
|航天飞机业余电台实验计划}}（{{lang-en|Shuttle Amateur Radio Experiment, SAREX}}）。随后，这一计划被{{tsl|en|Amateur Radio on the International Space Station
|国际空间站业余无线电计划}}（{{lang-en|Amateur Radio on the International Space Station, ARISS}}）继承<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dxcoffee.com/eng/2011/radio-space-beginning-sarex/ |title=Radio in space: in the Beginning there was SAREX |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=Mark Kelley |date=2011-08-10 |publisher=DxCoffee |language=en-US |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709154705/http://www.dxcoffee.com/eng/2011/radio-space-beginning-sarex/ |archivedate=2018-07-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]上的许多[[宇航员|宇航员]]同时也是拥有执照的业余无线电操作员，他们不时与地面的业余电台通联。学校可以向ARISS申请约定时间与空间站通联，为学生提供与宇航员直接通话的机会<ref name="ARISS">{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/ARISS/ |title=ARISS: Amateur Radio on the International Space Station |work=ARRL.org |accessdate=2007-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070111032250/http://www.arrl.org/ARISS/ |archivedate=2007-01-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="astrohams">{{cite web |url=http://users.tellurian.com/gjurrens/astrohams.html |title=Astronaut (and Former Astronaut) Hams |work=gjurrens ''at'' Tellurian.com |first=Gerald |last=Jurrens |accessdate=2007-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061230122251/http://users.tellurian.com/gjurrens/astrohams.html |archivedate=2006-12-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===应急通信===
业余无线电是应急通信的重要手段<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://handle.itu.int/11.1002/pub/800c8179-a399dce2-en |title=The Amateur Radio Service |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=ITU |date=2005 |work=Handbook on Emergency Telecommunications |publisher=International Telecommunication Union |pages=51 - 61 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121818/https://www.itu-ilibrary.org/science-and-technology/handbook-on-emergency-telecommunications_pub/800c8179-a399dce2-en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相较于商业无线电系统，业余无线电在抗毁性方面具有明显的优势。业余无线电是分散于民间的通信资源，以具备一定无线电技术的业余爱好者和业余电台作为独立的运作单元，经过适当训练的爱好者可以自行完成架设天线、设置电台和排除故障的任务，在灾害发生后可以以最小的需求迅速开通联络<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%2589%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%25BA%2594%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25AE%25AD%25E7%25BB%2583%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AF%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BA%25B2.pdf |title=《全国业余无线电应急通信训练指导大纲》建议稿 |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=中国无线电协会业余无线电工作委员会 |date=2013-07 |work=《业余无线电在应急信息发布中的应用研究分课题研究报告》 |publisher=中国无线电协会业余无线电工作委员会 |language=zh-CN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709123608/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%2589%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%25BA%2594%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25AE%25AD%25E7%25BB%2583%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AF%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BA%25B2.pdf/ |archivedate=2018-07-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=crac_emcomm>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258A%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25BA%2594%25E6%2580%25A5%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%258F%2591%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25BB%259F%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25BB%259F%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258A%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2595%25B4%25E4%25BD%2593%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588.pdf |title=《业余无线电在应急信息发布中的应用研究报告》 |accessdate=2018-07-09 |author=中国无线电协会业余无线电工作委员会 |date=2013-07 |format= |work=《公共应急信息无线电发布系统研究课题》 |language=zh-CN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709123554/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258A%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25BA%2594%25E6%2580%25A5%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%258F%2591%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25BB%259F%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25BB%259F%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258A%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2595%25B4%25E4%25BD%2593%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588.pdf/ |archivedate=2018-07-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/amateur-radio-emergency-communication |title=Amateur Radio Emergency Service |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=ARRL |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815140008/http://www.arrl.org/amateur-radio-emergency-communication |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。此外，全球的业余电台共用频率资源，每一时刻都有一定数目的电台在频率上守听，许多爱好者也对微弱信号有良好的分辨能力，这使得灾区发出的求救信号更容易获得回应<ref name=crac_emcomm/>。

===竞赛===
为了挑战自我、检验技术，许多业余无线电操作员参与业余无线电竞赛，在竞赛中，个人或团队通常需要在特定时间内在尽量多的波段上寻找尽可能多的电台并于他们通联<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/contest-basics |title=Contest Basics |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=ARRL |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815175957/http://www.arrl.org/contest-basics |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。国际上有许多此类“空中”的竞赛<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dxawards.com/ |title=K1BV DX Awards Directory |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=Ted Melinosky |date=2017 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815181825/http://www.dxawards.com/ |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。

===奖状===
全世界有关业余电台的奖状有数百种，这些旨在鼓励和表彰在远距离通信和各种通信试验中取得成绩的爱好者的证书,都是由各国或国际的业余无线电组织颁发的。当一个业余电台按照相关奖项的规则要求联络到足够数量的电台，并有对方寄来的QSL卡片或符合要求的网上确认通联凭证（如LOTW、EQSL等）时,就可以向颁发该奖状的协会提出申请<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/953252675 |title=业余无线电通信 |last=童 |first=效勇 |last2=陈 |first2=方 |date=2015-06 |publisher=人民邮电出版社 |year=2015 |isbn=9787115386359 |edition=第四版 |location=北京 |pages=83 |chapter=业余电台的奖励证书和竞赛活动|oclc=953252675 |access-date=2022-04-08 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121829/https://www.worldcat.org/title/ye-yu-wu-xian-dian-tong-xin-di-si-ban/oclc/953252675 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===新手===
许多人从寻找当地的俱乐部开始业余无线电生涯，俱乐部通常能提供有关执照的信息、当地的操作习惯以及技术指导<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/news/why-join-an-amateur-radio-club |title=Why Join an Amateur Radio Club |accessdate=2018-08-19 |author=Geoff Haines, N1GY |date=2009-06-03 |work=www.arrl.org |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819214227/http://www.arrl.org/news/why-join-an-amateur-radio-club |archive-date=2018-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.kb6nu.com/why-you-should-join-an-amateur-radio-club/ |title=Why you should join an amateur radio club - KB6NU's Ham Radio Blog |accessdate=2018-08-19 |author=Daniel M. Romanchik, KB6NU |date=2010-01-19 |work=KB6NU's Ham Radio Blog |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819182404/https://www.kb6nu.com/why-you-should-join-an-amateur-radio-club/ |archive-date=2018-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新手也常买书或利用其他资料自学，有时借助老手的帮助，帮助新手入门的老火腿在英语国家的火腿族中通常被称作“Elmer”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.na0tc.org/Tech_Elmer.html |title=285 TechConnect Radio Club |publisher=Na0tc.org |date= |accessdate=2012-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315234128/http://www.na0tc.org/Tech_Elmer.html |archivedate=2015-03-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/FandES/field/club/mentor/ |title=ARRL Mentor Program |work=ARRL.org |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014063645/http://www.arrl.org/FandES/field/club/mentor/ |archivedate=2007-10-14 |accessdate=2017-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=The ARRL Handbook for Radio Communications 2007 |publisher=American Radio Relay League |location={{tsl|en|Newington, CT|纽明顿（康涅狄格州）|Newington, CT}} |first=Mark J |last=Wilson |author2=Reed, Dana G |year=2006 |edition=84th |isbn=0-87259-976-0}}</ref>。在本地俱乐部的基础上，许多国家也建立了全国性的业余无线电协会<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iaru.org/member-societies.html |title=IARU Member Societies |accessdate=2017-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528020820/http://www.iaru.org/member-societies.html |archivedate=2017-05-28 }}</ref>，协会鼓励新手参加业余无线电活动，与政府通信管理部门合作促进业余无线电的发展<ref name="CRACobjectives">{{Cite web |url=http://www.crac.org.cn/?page_id=699 |title=CRAC简介 |accessdate=2018-05-30 |author=中国无线电协会业余无线电分会 |work=www.crac.org.cn |language=zh-CN |quote=CRAC将竭诚为我国业余无线电的健康发展努力，当好管理部门的助手，尽力为广大业余无线电爱好者服务。 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608083551/http://www.crac.org.cn/?page_id=699 |archivedate=2018-06-08 }}</ref>。

==许可==
{{legal}}
[[File:Amateur_Radio_License_of_People's_Republic_of_China_(Fixed_Station).jpg|thumb]]
[[File:USA_FCC_Amateur_Radio_License.jpg|thumb]]
无线电波的传播不因国界而停止，属于国际事务，并且存在潜在的[[地下电台|地下非法使用]]，因此无线电业务在各国都被政府严格管控。这一情况也适用于业余无线电，因此，业余无线电爱好者必须申请许可和执照才能合法开展业余无线电活动。业余无线电执照及操作权利的管理法规因国家而异，但总体来说遵循[[国际电信联盟|国际电信联盟]]和[[世界无线电行政会议|世界无线电行政会议]]（WARC）确立的国际条例和标准<ref name=ituars>{{cite web |url=http://life.itu.int/radioclub/ars.htm |title=Amateur and Amateur-satellite service |publisher=International Telecommunication Union |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100822233356/http://life.itu.int/radioclub/ars.htm |archivedate=2010-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="itu_exam_rec">{{Citation |author=国际电信联盟 |title=业余无线电爱好者的基本要求 |date=2016-12-02 |url=https://www.itu.int/dms_pubrec/itu-r/rec/m/R-REC-M.1544-1-201509-I!!PDF-C.pdf |number=ITU-R M.1544-1 |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2018-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705181609/https://www.itu.int/dms_pubrec/itu-r/rec/m/R-REC-M.1544-1-201509-I!!PDF-C.pdf |archivedate=2018-07-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

所有允许国民申请业余无线电执照的国家都要求操作员对基本知识和要点有足够的了解，以通过考试作为判断标准<ref name="ham_exam">{{Cite web|url=http://www.xcwxd.gov.cn/show.asp?id=68|title=怎样成为业余无线电爱好者|accessdate=2017-08-16|author=山东无线电管理办公室|date=2011-07-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816110602/http://www.xcwxd.gov.cn/show.asp?id=68|archivedate=2017-08-16}}</ref><ref name="itu_exam_rec"/>。业余无线电执照赋予了火腿族在相对较广的业余[[无线电频率|无线电频率]]上操作，广泛使用各式无线电技术，以及使用相对于免执照公众业务{{noteTag|1=例如[[民用波段无线电台|民用波段无线电台]]、{{tsl|en|Family Radio Service|家用无线电业务}}以及{{tsl|en|PMR446|PMR446}}。}}更高的发射功率的权力，但通常也要求仅使用经过核准的模式、工作频率且功率合规的设备<ref name="bandplan">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/band-plan |title=Band Plan |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=ARRL |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816105953/http://www.arrl.org/band-plan |archivedate=2017-08-16 }}</ref><ref name="USbands">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/files/file/Regulatory/Band%20Chart/Hambands4-web-color_4-25-17.pdf |title=US Amateur Radio Bands |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=ARRL |date=2017-04-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816110355/http://www.arrl.org/files/file/Regulatory/Band%20Chart/Hambands4-web-color_4-25-17.pdf |archivedate=2017-08-16 }}</ref><ref name="rigs">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nantong.gov.cn/art/2015/3/30/art_56089_1854568.html |title=业余电台为何要验机？检验哪些指标？ |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=缪晗 |date=2015-03-30 |publisher=南通市人民政府 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816111511/http://www.nantong.gov.cn/art/2015/3/30/art_56089_1854568.html |archivedate=2017-08-16 }}</ref>。

业余无线电爱好者必须通过考试以取得业余无线电执照<ref name="ham_exam"></ref>。执照考试又通常分为多级，更高级的考试通常更具挑战性，通过更高级的考试后爱好者可以获得更多的操作权限<ref name="USbands"></ref>：更多频段、更高发射功率、允许进行通信实验，以及在一些国家可获得能体现等级的高级呼号{{noteTag|1=更短的或带高级前缀的呼号。}}<ref name=callsign_class>{{Cite web |url=http://www.w5yi.org/page.php?id=281 |title=Vanity Call Signs FAQ : What are Call Sign Groups |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=W5YI-VEC |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816111616/http://www.w5yi.org/page.php?id=281 |archivedate=2017-08-16 }}</ref>。在一些国家，爱好者在通过笔试的基础上还要通过实际操作考试，才能取得执照<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://amateurradio.com.au/sites/default/files/basicpage/aocpf-syllabus.pdf |title=Amateur Operator's Certificate of Proficiency (Foundation) Syllabus and Examination |accessdate=2017-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217211647/https://www.amateurradio.com.au/sites/default/files/basicpage/aocpf-syllabus.pdf |archivedate=2017-02-17 }}</ref>。

在大多数国家，在给爱好者颁发执照的同时，管理机构还会给业余无线电操作员指配一个[[业余无线电台呼号|呼号]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fcc.gov/wireless/bureau-divisions/mobility-division/amateur-radio-service/amateur-call-sign-systems |title=Amateur Call Sign Systems |accessdate=2017-08-22 |author=Federal Communications Commission |date=2016-09-28 |language=en |quote=A unique call sign is assigned to each amateur station during the processing of its license applications. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816160338/https://www.fcc.gov/wireless/bureau-divisions/mobility-division/amateur-radio-service/amateur-call-sign-systems |archivedate=2017-08-16 }}</ref>在一些国家，不光是爱好者本人，爱好者操作的业余业务电台也需要获颁台站执照（{{lang-en|station license}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/22588011|title=业余无线电爱好者必须知道的事儿——关于电台执照的问与答|accessdate=2017-08-22|author=中特人|date=2016-09-23|work=知乎专栏|publisher=知乎|language=zh-CN|quote=所以说，呼号是印在电台执照上的，是指配给检测合格的电台的。|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822174228/https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/22588011|archivedate=2017-08-22}}</ref>。组织和俱乐部也可以获颁业余无线电执照。在一些国家、一些条件下，火腿族只被允许操作集体电台<ref name="CQ现代通信">{{Cite magazine |title=见证共和国业余无线电发展的人：专访童晓勇/BA1AA |author=鲍沁勇、徐璟华、林森 |journal=CQ现代通信 |publisher=北京博趣出版有限责任公司 |accessdate=2017-07-05 |issue=2017第2期 |year=2017 |page=65 |language=zh-cn |issn=1000-6559}}</ref><ref>{{cite wikisource |title=业余无线电台管理暂行规定 |year= 1982 |publisher=国家体育运动委员会, 国家无线电管理委员会 |wslanguage= zh}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258E%2586%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6.doc |title=我国业余无线电管理体制历史研究 |accessdate=2018-07-14 |author=中国无线电协会业余无线电工作委员会 |date=2011-07-13 |format=doc |language=zh-CN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714111512/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%259A%25E4%25BD%2599%25E6%2597%25A0%25E7%25BA%25BF%25E7%2594%25B5%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258E%2586%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6.doc/ |archivedate=2018-07-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

业余无线电执照只在颁发国和与颁发国签订了双边条约的国家中有效。在一些国家，如[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]和[[古巴|古巴]]，外国人只被允许操作集体电台 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.qsl.net/tir/Foreign%20Amateurs.htm |title=Foreign Amateurs in Syria |accessdate=2017-07-06 |author=SSTARS |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312043918/http://www.qsl.net/tir/Foreign%20Amateurs.htm |archivedate=2016-03-12 }}</ref>。

在一些国家，爱好者必须持有业余无线电执照才可以购买或拥有业余无线电设备<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.qsl.net/rast/text/licensing2010.html |title=Amateur radio licensing in Thailand – sect. Equipment license |publisher=The Radio Amateur Society of Thailand 7 August 2010 |accessdate=2011-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226041031/http://www.qsl.net/rast/text/licensing2010.html |archivedate=2011-02-26 }}</ref>。

[[File:老式中华人民共和国无线电台执照壳.jpg|thumb]]

===获得执照===
对个人来说，“准”业余无线电操作员需要参加考试<ref name="ham_exam"/>，以评估他们对于电子学的技术要点、无线电设备、天线、{{tsl|en|radio propagation|无线电传播}}、[[射频|射频]]安全以及所在国业余无线电法规等知识的了解程度<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/913316707 |title=电子达人：我的第一本业余无线电手册 |last=Silver |first=H. Ward |last2=赵 |first2=正 |publisher=人民邮电出版社 |year=2014 |isbn=9787115364173 |edition=第二版 |location=北京 |pages=55-56 |chapter=揭开考试的神秘面纱 |oclc=913316707 |access-date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121821/https://www.worldcat.org/title/dian-zi-da-ren-wo-de-di-yi-ben-ye-yu-wu-xian-dian-shou-ce/oclc/913316707 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="itu_exam_rec"/>。考试通常是以选择题的形式呈现<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dummies.com/programming/ham-radio/what-to-expect-the-day-of-your-ham-radio-license-test/ |title=What to Expect the Day of Your Ham Radio License Test |accessdate=2018-07-06 |author=H. Ward Silver |work=dummies |publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc. |language=en-US |quote=The exams are multiple-choice tests. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706075028/https://www.dummies.com/programming/ham-radio/what-to-expect-the-day-of-your-ham-radio-license-test/ |archivedate=2018-07-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。考试一般由[[政府官员|政府官员]]、获准的义务考官或者已经获颁执照的操作员主办<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/913316707 |title=电子达人：我的第一本业余无线电手册 |last=Silver |first=H. Ward |last2=赵 |first2=正 |publisher=人民邮电出版社 |year=2014 |isbn=9787115364173 |edition=第二版 |location=北京 |pages=63-64 |chapter=第六章：参加许可考试 |oclc=913316707 |access-date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121822/https://www.worldcat.org/title/dian-zi-da-ren-wo-de-di-yi-ben-ye-yu-wu-xian-dian-shou-ce/oclc/913316707 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2014-0512%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%9A%E4%BD%99%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A.doc|title=业余无线电台操作技术能力验证机构信息公告|accessdate=2017-08-22|author=中国无线电协会业余无线电分会|date=2014-05-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822221839/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2014-0512%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%9A%E4%BD%99%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A.doc|archivedate=2017-08-22}}</ref>。个人获得业余无线电执照的难易程度因国家而异。在一些国家，执照考试每年只在国家首都举办一到两次，并且办理执照的流程有着许多繁文缛节，爱好者可能还需要通过非常复杂的安全审查<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-procedure-to-obtain-Ham-Radio-license-in-India/answer/Sachin-Perinthalakkat |title=Sachin Perinthalakkat's answer to What is the procedure to obtain Ham Radio license in India? - Quora |accessdate=2018-08-19 |author=Sachin Perinthalakkat |date=2017-11-09 |language=en}}</ref>。目前，仅有[[也门|也门]]和[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜]]不向公民颁发业余无线电执照，但是这两个国家在前十年间都有允许外国游客操作业余无线电的前例<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/news/north-korea-on-the-air-for-first-time-since-2002 |title=North Korea on the Air for First Time Since 2002 |accessdate=2017-07-07 |author=ARRL |date=2015-12-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423152419/http://www.arrl.org/news/north-korea-on-the-air-for-first-time-since-2002 |archivedate=2016-04-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/news/7o6t-yemen-dxpedition-to-get-underway-today |title=7O6T Yemen DXpedition to Get Underway Today |accessdate=2017-07-07 |author=ARRL |date=2012-04-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150802041608/http://www.arrl.org/news/7o6t-yemen-dxpedition-to-get-underway-today |archivedate=2015-08-02 }}</ref>。在一些有着大量业余无线电操作员的国家，例如[[美国|美国]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]，爱好者可以很方便地参加执照考试<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/find-an-amateur-radio-license-exam-session |title=Find an Amateur Radio License Exam in Your Area |accessdate=2018-08-19 |author=ARRL |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819214233/http://www.arrl.org/find-an-amateur-radio-license-exam-session |archive-date=2018-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

向俱乐部或者组织颁发集体业余无线电执照，通常要求一位当前执照有效、在电信管理机构拥有良好信誉的业余无线电操作员对使用集体电台或呼号进行的任何操作承担责任<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/club-call-signs |title=Club Call Signs |accessdate=2017-10-04 |author=ARRL |work=www.arrl.org |language=en |quote=A club station license is granted only to the person who is the license trustee designated by an officer of the club. The trustee must be a person who holds an operator/primary station license grant. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010171306/http://www.arrl.org/club-call-signs |archivedate=2017-10-10 }}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Amateur radio licensing in the United States|美国业余无线电执照制度}}在根据技能水平分等级颁发业余无线电执照的各国中较具代表性。美国目前颁发的执照共有三个等级，从低到高分别是技术员级、普通级和业余特级（{{lang-en|Technician Class, General Class, and Amateur Extra Class}}），更高的等级开放了更多的操作频率<ref name="bandplan" />和更高级或更短的呼号<ref name="callsign_class" />。所有等级都需要通过由联邦通信委员会（FCC）核准的考试。考试由志愿考官（{{lang-en|'''V'''olunteer '''E'''xaminer, VE}}）主办<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/871320539 |title=ARRL/VEC VOLUNTEER EXAMINER MANUAL |last=Palm |first=Richard |last2=Somma |first2=Maria |publisher=The American Radio Relay League, Inc |year=2013 |isbn=0872591328 |edition=Ninth edition |location=Newington, Connecticut |pages=10 |language=en-us |chapter=Volunteer Examiner (VE) |oclc=871320539 |quote=Examination sessions must be coordinated by a VEC, but are conducted in the field by VEs. |access-date=2017-10-05 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121820/https://www.worldcat.org/title/arrlvec-volunteer-examiner-manual-your-complete-guide-to-the-arrl-amateur-radio-volunteer-examiner-program/oclc/871320539 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，志愿考官由志愿考官协调委员会（{{lang-en|'''V'''olunteer '''E'''xaminer '''C'''oordinator, VEC}}）任命<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/871320539 |title=ARRL/VEC VOLUNTEER EXAMINER MANUAL |last=Palm |first=Richard |last2=Somma |first2=Maria |publisher=The American Radio Relay League, Inc |year=2013 |isbn=0872591328 |edition=Ninth edition |location=Newington, Connecticut |pages=10 |language=en-us |chapter=Volunteer Examiner (VE) |oclc=871320539 |quote=Volunteer Examiners (VEs) are individuals accredited by a VEC |access-date=2017-10-05 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121820/https://www.worldcat.org/title/arrlvec-volunteer-examiner-manual-your-complete-guide-to-the-arrl-amateur-radio-volunteer-examiner-program/oclc/871320539 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而协调委员会需要FCC的批准<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/871320539 |title=ARRL/VEC VOLUNTEER EXAMINER MANUAL |last=Palm |first=Richard |last2=Somma |first2=Maria |publisher=The American Radio Relay League, Inc |year=2013 |isbn=0872591328 |edition=Ninth edition |location=Newington, Connecticut |pages=10 |language=en-us |chapter=Volunteer Examiner Coordinator (VEC) |oclc=871320539 |quote=No organization may serve as a VEC unless it has entered into a written agreement with the FCC. |access-date=2017-10-05 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121824/https://www.worldcat.org/title/arrlvec-volunteer-examiner-manual-your-complete-guide-to-the-arrl-amateur-radio-volunteer-examiner-program/oclc/871320539 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。技术员级和普通级考试共需回答35道从至少350题的题库中随机抽取的选择题，并且需要至少答对26道。<ref name="FCC Amateur Exam">{{cite web |url=http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=licensing_2&id=amateur |title=Amateur Licensing Examinations |publisher=Federal Communications Commission |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529221252/http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=licensing_2&id=amateur |archivedate=2016-05-29 |accessdate=2017-07-07 }}</ref>业余特级考试包含50道选择题（从至少500道题的题库中随机抽取），考生需要至少答对37道题以通过考试<ref name="FCC Amateur Exam" />。考试范围覆盖了法规、操作习惯以及技术知识，例如法规、操作程序、电子学知识、电台设计以及安全知识<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/files/file/Instructor%20resources/Technician%20Class/Technician%20rev%203-10.pdf |title=Technician License Syllabus |accessdate=2018-06-08 |author=Jack Tiley, AD7FO |date=2012-07-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812030354/http://www.arrl.org/files/file/Instructor%20resources/Technician%20Class/Technician%20rev%203-10.pdf |archivedate=2016-08-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。摩尔斯电码报务技术在美国已经不再需要考核<ref name="morsedropped1"/>。一旦通过考试，FCC将会给考生颁发十年有效期的业余无线电执照。题库每四年由全国志愿考官协调委员会（{{lang-en|National Conference of VECs}}）更新一次<ref name="FCC Amateur Exam" />。

在[[中华人民共和国业余无线电执照制度|中国大陆]]，业余无线电爱好者必须首先考取操作证书（共分A类、B类、C类。C类证书级别最高）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/2013-0301-%E4%B8%9A%E4%BD%99%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95_CRAC%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E7%89%88_.pdf|title=业余无线电台操作技术能力验证暂行办法|accessdate=2017-07-07|author=中国无线电协会|date=2013-03-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816112218/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/2013-0301-%E4%B8%9A%E4%BD%99%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95_CRAC%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E7%89%88_.pdf|archivedate=2017-08-16}}</ref>，然后申领执照，若设备没有核准代码，需要再由地方无线电管理机构验机<ref name="rigs"/>。爱好者获颁执照后方能发射。中华人民共和国《业余无线电台管理办法》已经明确不用再加入任何协会就可以考取业余无线电操作证书，取得证书后便可以申请业余无线电执照<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gov.cn/flfg/2012-11/08/content_2260255.htm | title=中华人民共和国工业和信息化部令 第22号 《业余无线电台管理办法》 | accessdate=2015-04-14 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130201030224/http://www.gov.cn/flfg/2012-11/08/content_2260255.htm | archivedate=2013-02-01 }}</ref>。

在[[臺灣地區|臺灣地區]]，依據中華民國《業餘無線電管理辦法》: “第二十八條，業餘電台應經申請取得電台執照後始得使用。第三十條，業餘電台之呼號，除臨時電台由交通部直接指配外，其他電台之呼號於申設業餘電台時，由電信監理資訊系統自動產生，任何人員皆不得要求指配特定呼號。業餘無線電人員取得較高等級之資格後，原設置之業餘電台得申請改配呼號<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=K0060032 |title=業餘無線電管理辦法 |accessdate=2017-10-04 |author=國家通訊傳播委員會 |date=2007-07-13 |language=zh-tw |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502182300/https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=K0060032 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

===跨国操作===
{{main article|{{tsl|en|Amateur radio international operation|业余无线电跨国操作}}}}
[[File:Amateur Radio International Agreements.png|right|300px|thumb|<center>'''各国参与业余无线电双边协议情况'''</center>
{{legend|#c4000a|CEPT成员国}}
{{legend|#f2f204|IARP成员国}}
{{legend|orange|CEPT与IARP成员国}}
{{legend|#00ff00|美加协议、CEPT与IARP成员国}}]]

一般来说，一国颁发的业余无线电执照只在本国管辖范围内有效，前往其他国家操作电台应当办理到访国的业余无线电执照<ref name="USOverseas" />。然而，许多国家签订了双边条约，使得有执照的业余无线电操作员无需考取、办理到访国的执照，或者直接换发执照便可以在该国境内合法地操作业余电台<ref name="CEPT"/><ref name="IARP">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oas.org/en/sla/dil/inter_american_treaties_A-62_international_radio_permit.asp |title=Inter-American Convention on an International Amateur Radio Permit |accessdate=2018-08-20 |author=Inter-American Telecommunication Commission |date=2009-08-01 |work=www.oas.org |language=en |id=A-62 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820172618/http://www.oas.org/en/sla/dil/inter_american_treaties_A-62_international_radio_permit.asp |archive-date=2018-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。双边执照认可的要求因国家而异。一些国家加入了多边条约<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cept.org/cept/cept-members-units-and-admission-year |title=CEPT Members, units and admission year |accessdate=2018-08-20 |author=European Conference of Postal and Telecommunications Administrations |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820172953/https://www.cept.org/cept/cept-members-units-and-admission-year |archive-date=2018-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因此执照在各缔约国内都有效<ref name="CEPT">{{Cite book |url=https://www.ecodocdb.dk/download/e4b9c459-5726/TR6102%20.pdf |title=Harmonised Amateur Radio Examination Certificate |author=The European Conference of Postal and Telecommunications Administrations |year=2003 |id=T/R 61-02 |access-date=2018-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509013130/https://www.ecodocdb.dk/download/e4b9c459-5726/TR6102%20.pdf |archive-date=2018-05-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="IARP"/>。

跨国操作时，来访操作员必须遵守所在国的法规。一些国家允许来访的火腿族仅持有[[母国|母国]]的执照便可以进行操作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/cept |title=European Conference of Postal & Telecommunications Administrations (CEPT) |accessdate=2017-10-03 |author=ARRL |work=www.arrl.org |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003075841/http://www.arrl.org/cept |archivedate=2017-10-03 }}</ref>。另一些国家要求来访的操作员提前申请操作许可或换发本国执照<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crac.org.cn/?p=1646 |title=The Application Procedure for "AMATEUR RADIO OPERATOR'S CERTIFICATE FOR VISITORS"   |accessdate=2017-10-03 |author=中国无线电协会业余无线电分会 |date=2013-06-30 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003124519/http://www.crac.org.cn/?p=1646 |archivedate=2017-10-03 }}</ref>。 

执照的双边承认不仅取决于发照的国家，还可能取决于持照人的国籍<ref name="USOverseas" />。举例来说，在美国，只有当操作员的国籍非美国，且并不持有美国执照{{NoteTag|1=持有美国执照可能导致操作权利和限制的区别，举例来说，如果一位无线电操作员持有中国大陆的C类操作证，却只持有Technician级美国执照时，他只能按照Technician级的操作权利在美国进行操作。}}时，他的外国执照才被认可<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/foreign-licenses-operating-in-u-s |title=Foreign Licenses Operating in U.S. |accessdate=2017-07-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803181208/http://www.arrl.org/foreign-licenses-operating-in-u-s |archivedate=2017-08-03 }}</ref>。持有执照的美国公民可以直接按照双边协议在互惠条约的缔约国操作，但持有美国执照的外国公民并不能享受这一权利<ref name="USOverseas">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/us-amateurs-operating-overseas |title=US Amateurs Operating Overseas |accessdate=2017-07-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170611191541/http://www.arrl.org/us-amateurs-operating-overseas |archivedate=2017-06-11 }}</ref>。

===呼号===
{{Further|业余无线电呼号|業餘無線電呼號前綴列表}}
业余无线电操作员在无线电通信中以“呼号”唯一地表明自己或台站的身份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ofcom.org.uk/static/archive/ra/publication/ra_info/br68i/br68i.htm |title=Amateur Radio (Intermediate) License (A) or (B) Terms, Provisions and Limitations Booklet BR68/I |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930034504/http://www.ofcom.org.uk/static/archive/ra/publication/ra_info/br68i/br68i.htm |archivedate=2007-09-30 |accessdate=2017-07-07 }}</ref>。在一些国家，通联时只能使用指配给台站的呼号，而在其他国家，操作员和台站的呼号任选其一使用<ref name="amateurlicences">{{cite web |url=http://www.ofcom.org.uk/static/archive/ra/publication/ra_info/br68i/br68i.htm |title=Amateur Radio (Intermediate) License (A) or (B) Terms, Provisions and Limitations Booklet BR68/I |work=Ofcom.org.uk |accessdate=2007-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930034504/http://www.ofcom.org.uk/static/archive/ra/publication/ra_info/br68i/br68i.htm |archivedate=2007-09-30 }}</ref>。在特定的地区，操作员可以自选呼号（{{lang-en|vanity callsign}}），但自选必须服从所在国的前缀、呼号指配的情况以及呼号等级的规定<ref name="vanity">{{cite web |url=http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=cft&id=amateur&page=cft_get_call_sign |title=Common Filing Task: Obtaining Vanity Call Sign |work=FCC.gov |accessdate=2007-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070827155210/http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=cft&id=amateur&page=cft_get_call_sign |archivedate=2007-08-27 }}</ref>。一些地区要求缴纳一定费用以自选呼号<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wia.org.au/licenses/licensing/guidetocallsigns/ |title=Guide To Callsigns |accessdate=2018-07-02 |author=Wireless Institute of Austrialia |date=2018-06-04 |work=www.wia.org.au |quote=Level Two [Selected two, three or four letter callsign, except two letter callsigns in Vic, NSW & QLD] $20 including GST |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401195507/http://www.wia.org.au/licenses/licensing/guidetocallsigns/ |archivedate=2018-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而在其他一些国家，例如英国，自选呼号无需额外费用，而且在申请执照时就可自选。美国联邦通信委员会在2015年9月取消了自选呼号的收费<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/vanity-call-sign-fees |title=Vanity Call Sign Fees |work=ARRL.org |accessdate=2015-09-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929092348/http://www.arrl.org/vanity-call-sign-fees |archivedate=2015-09-29 }}</ref>。

国际电信联盟规定的呼号结构由以下三个部分组成<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wia.org.au/licenses/licensing/callsignstructure/ |title=Amateur Callsign Structure |accessdate=2017-07-07 |author=WIA |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114162221/http://www.wia.org.au/licenses/licensing/callsignstructure/ |archivedate=2017-01-14 }}</ref>，以下以呼号'''ZS1NAT'''为例：
* '''ZS'''——前缀，表示呼号所属的国家。（这个呼号为南非呼号<ref name="ZS">{{Cite web |url=http://www.sarl.org.za/ZSZones.asp |title=ZS Callsign Zones |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=South African Radio League |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627230237/http://www.sarl.org.za/ZSZones.asp |archivedate=2017-06-27 }}</ref>）臨時跨國操作時，呼号前會增加所在地的前綴，比如在香港操作时，ZS1NAT的呼号应当变为'''VR2/ZS1NAT'''。
* '''1'''——分区号，表示国家内部的分区。（这里的'''1'''表示西开普省<ref name="ZS"/>）
* '''NAT'''——后缀，用于区分不同的业余电台。

许多国家并不按照ITU常规使用呼号中的数字部分。英国不使用数字区分国家内部的分区，而是使用前缀“G”后的第二位字母<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.electronics-notes.com/articles/ham_radio/call-signs/uk-amateur-radio-callsigns.php |title=UK Amateur Radio Callsigns |accessdate=2017-08-16 |author=electronics-notes.com |work=www.electronics-notes.com |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017144010/https://www.electronics-notes.com/articles/ham_radio/call-signs/uk-amateur-radio-callsigns.php |archivedate=2016-10-17 }}</ref>；举例来说，G7OOE在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]操作时呼号应当变为GM7OOE。前缀GM代表苏格兰，G或GE（“E”通常省略）代表[[英格兰|英格兰]]，而GW代表[[威尔士|威尔士]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ofcom.gov.uk |title=UK Radio & Media Licensing Authority (''Ofcom'') website |accessdate=2017-07-06 |author=UK Radio & Media Licensing Authority |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040627080852/http://www.ofcom.gov.uk/ |archivedate=2004-06-27 }}</ref>。对于较小的政治实体，数字部分可能也是国家前缀的一部分。例如VP2代表[[英属西印度群岛|英属西印度群岛]]<ref name="callprefix">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ac6v.com/prefixes.htm |title=Amateur Radio Prefixes |accessdate=2017-08-16 |work=www.ac6v.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627235235/http://www.ac6v.com/prefixes.htm |archivedate=2017-06-27 }}</ref>，并且可以继续细分为VP2E（[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]）、VP2M（[[蒙特塞拉特|蒙特塞拉特]]）以及VP2V（[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]）。VP5代表[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]，VP6代表[[皮特凯恩群岛|皮特凯恩群岛]]，VP8代表[[福克兰群岛|福克兰群岛]]，而VP9代表[[百慕大|百慕大]]<ref name="callprefix" />。

在线{{tsl|en|callbook|呼号手册}}可以协助查找特定呼号的持有者<ref>{{cite web |title=License Search |url=http://wireless2.fcc.gov/UlsApp/UlsSearch/searchLicense.jsp |work=Universal Licensing System |publisher=US Federal Communications Commission |accessdate=2010-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100822154313/http://wireless2.fcc.gov/UlsApp/UlsSearch/searchLicense.jsp |archivedate=2010-08-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。举例来说，{{tsl|en|QRZ.COM|QRZ.COM}}就是一个著名的在线呼号手册。也有组织出版拥有呼号的著名人士名单<ref>{{cite web |title=Famous Radio Amateurs 'Hams' & Call Signs |url=http://www.bedworthlionsclub.co.uk/abtamfam.htm |publisher=Bedworth Lions Club |accessdate=2010-08-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100831041650/http://www.bedworthlionsclub.co.uk/abtamfam.htm |archivedate=2010-08-31 }}</ref>。

一些地区，如美国，为持有执照的业余无线电操作员发放呼号[[车辆号牌|车牌]]，以增加他们在紧急情况下的机动能力<ref name="ARRL-plates">{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/FandES/field/regulations/local/plates.html |title=ARRL Web: Amateur Radio License Plate Fees |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070804045533/http://www.arrl.org/FandES/field/regulations/local/plates.html |archivedate=2007-08-04 |accessdate=2017-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://plates.hfradio.net/plate1.html |title=Ham Radio Callsign License Plates (Canada) |accessdate=2008-12-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207083448/http://plates.hfradio.net/plate1.html |archivedate=2008-12-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。申请和续期牌照的费用通常比自选牌照低<ref name="ARRL-plates"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.icbc.com/registration/reg_spec_lic_plates_ham.asp |title=ICBC – HAM radio plates |accessdate=2008-12-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081019175012/http://www.icbc.com/registration/reg_spec_lic_plates_ham.asp |archivedate=2008-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===操作权利===
[[File:Montreal-tower-top.thumb2-crop.jpg|thumb]]和多副短波长线天线的塔顶]]
在大多数地区，有别于其他无线电使用者，业余无线电爱好者可以自制或改装他们的设备<ref name="homemade">{{Cite web |url=https://makezine.com/2015/06/30/a-makers-introduction-to-ham-radio/ |title=A Maker's Introduction to Ham Radio |accessdate=2017-09-23 |author=Ward Silver |date=2015-06-30 |work=Make: DIY Projects and Ideas for Makers |publisher=Maker Media, Inc. |language=en-US |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924001534/https://makezine.com/2015/06/30/a-makers-introduction-to-ham-radio/ |archivedate=2017-09-24 }}</ref>，以满足他们在业余频段上的操作需求，这通常无需政府核准<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ofta.gov.hk/en/rae/rae0101E_F.pdf |title=OFTA, Equipment for Amateur Station: ''Radio amateurs are free to choose any radio equipment designed for the amateur service. Radio amateurs may also design and build their own equipment provided that the requirements and limitations specified in the Amateur Station Licence and Schedules thereto are complied with. '' |accessdate=2017-07-07 |archive-date=2007-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014040938/http://www.ofta.gov.hk/en/rae/rae0101E_F.pdf |dead-url=yes }}{{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014040938/http://www.ofta.gov.hk/en/rae/rae0101E_F.pdf |date=2007-10-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=about&id=amateur |title=FCC.gov, About Amateur Stations. 'They design, construct, modify, and repair their stations. The FCC equipment authorization program does not generally apply to amateur station transmitters.' |publisher=Wireless.fcc.gov |date=2002-02-19 |accessdate=2012-11-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121213004027/http://wireless.fcc.gov/services/index.htm?job=about&id=amateur |archivedate=2012-12-13 }}</ref>。持有执照的爱好者还可以使用任意批准使用的业余频段（而非某个特定的频点），并且可以在较广的频率范围内使用较高功率的设备<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vkfaq.ampr.org/faq2lic.html |title=Australian Radio Amateur FAQ |work=AMPR.org |date=2006-06-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080718193714/http://vkfaq.ampr.org/faq2lic.html |archivedate=2008-07-18 |accessdate=2017-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，只要其设备满足例如带宽、功率、{{tsl|en|spurious emission|杂散辐射}}等的技术参数要求<ref name="rigs"/>。

====频段====
业余无线电爱好者可以使用无线电频谱内所有分配的业余业务频段，通常频段选择由通联范围所决定<ref name="band_choice"></ref>。短波波段，或称作[[高频|HF]]，适合全球范围的通联<ref name="band_choice"></ref>，而[[甚高频|VHF]]和[[特高频|UHF]]适用于本地通联<ref name="band_choice">{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/953252675 |title=业余无线电通信 |last=童 |first=效勇 |last2=陈 |first2=方 |date=2015-06 |publisher=人民邮电出版社 |year=2015 |isbn=9787115386359 |edition=第四版 |location=北京 |pages=111-113 |chapter=怎样利用不同的业余波段 |oclc=953252675 |access-date=2017-07-07 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121829/https://www.worldcat.org/title/ye-yu-wu-xian-dian-tong-xin-di-si-ban/oclc/953252675 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[微波|微波]]波段由于其带宽的优势，通常用于业余无线电电视和高速[[计算机网络|计算机网络]]链路<ref name="band_choice"></ref>。

====设备====
在大多数国家，持有业余无线电执照的爱好者可以持有、改装及操作未经管理部门核准的设备<ref name="homemade"/>。这鼓励了业余无线电操作员试验自制或修改的设备<ref name="homemade"/>。但这些设备也必须符合国际国内关于{{tsl|en|spurious emission|杂散辐射}}的标准<ref name="43号文件"/>和地點限制。

====功率====
业余无线电爱好者可以合法使用的最高发射[[功率|功率]]因国家而异。尽管[[功率|功率]]相比商业业务较低，但也足以进行全球范围通联。 功率限制因国家和执照等级而异。举例来说，在[[加拿大|加拿大]]，持有最高级执照的操作员可以使用高达2.25千[[瓦特|瓦]]的{{tsl|en|peak envelope power|包络峰值功率}}<ref name="Industry Canada">{{cite journal |url=http://www.ic.gc.ca/eic/site/smt-gst.nsf/eng/sf01226.html |title=RBR-4 – Standards for the Operation of Radio Stations in the Amateur Radio Service, s. 10.2 |date=September 2007 |accessdate=2013-01-21 |last=Industry Canada |publisher=Government of Canada |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113020113/http://www.ic.gc.ca/eic/site/smt-gst.nsf/eng/sf01226.html |archivedate=2013-01-13 |journal= }}</ref>，在[[美国|美国]]，业余无线电的功率上限为1.5千瓦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/frequency-allocations |title=US Amateur Transmitter Power Limits |accessdate=2017-09-15 |author=ARRL |work=www.arrl.org |language=en |quote=Unless otherwise noted, the maximum power output is 1500 watts PEP. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903165122/http://www.arrl.org/frequency-allocations |archivedate=2017-09-03 }}</ref>。较低的执照等级通常有较低的最高功率。按照规定和传统，为了防止干扰其他电台，业余无线电爱好者应当只使用能满足良好通联质量的最低功率<ref name="FCC section 97.313">{{cite web |url=http://www.w5yi.org/page.php?id=142 |title=FCC Part 97 : Sec. 97.313 Transmitter power standards |work=W5YI.org |accessdate=2010-08-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203020431/http://www.w5yi.org/page.php?id=142 |archivedate=2010-12-03 }}</ref>。

发射功率的限制也取决于通联模式。例如在澳大利亚，SSB模式可以使用最高400瓦，但FM模式只能使用120瓦<ref name="AUS">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/news/australia-ends-higher-power-trial-for-radio-amateurs |title=Australia Ends Higher Power Trial for Radio Amateurs |accessdate=2017-09-15 |author=ARRL |date=2013-08-26 |publisher=ARRL |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916013612/http://www.arrl.org/news/australia-ends-higher-power-trial-for-radio-amateurs |archivedate=2017-09-16 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vkfaq.ampr.org/lictypes.php |title=Licence Types and how to get the one you need |accessdate=2018-06-21 |author=Andrew Davis, VK1DA |date=2008 |work=Amateur Radio in Australia (VKFAQ) |quote=with power limits of 400 watts (PEP for SSB) and 120 watts (for constant carrier modes). |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002082453/http://vkfaq.ampr.org/lictypes.php |archivedate=2017-10-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

发射功率的测量方法也会影响实际可用的功率。例如英国规定发射功率在天线馈线接口处测量，因此发信设备可以发射超过400瓦的功率以克服馈线内的损耗。然而德国规定发射功率在发信设备的天线接口处测量，这导致了实际可用的功率因为馈线损耗而减小<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bundesnetzagentur.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/Areas/Telecommunications/Companies/TelecomRegulation/FrequencyManagement/AmateurRadio/AFuV_March2008_kurz_EN.pdf;jsessionid=6099172D03520691D98707E972F0B344?__blob=publicationFile&v=2 |title=Ordinance Concerning the Amateur Radio Act |accessdate=2017-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923132324/https://www.bundesnetzagentur.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/Areas/Telecommunications/Companies/TelecomRegulation/FrequencyManagement/AmateurRadio/AFuV_March2008_kurz_EN.pdf%3Bjsessionid%3D6099172D03520691D98707E972F0B344?__blob=publicationFile&v=2 |archivedate=2017-09-23 }}</ref>。

在某些波段（如{{tsl|en|2200-meter band|2200m}}，{{tsl|en|600-meter band|600m}}和{{tsl|en|60-meter band|60m}}），《无线电规则》限制了发射信号的[[等效全向辐射功率|等效全向辐射功率]]<ref name="RR"/>{{rp|at=5.67A 5.80A 5.133B}}。在这些波段实际能够使用的功率，由发信设备功率、馈线损耗和天线增益共同决定<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://apps.fcc.gov/kdb/GetAttachment.html?id=fzlsGm%2Fe68Ymx58IAmzNbw%3D%3D&desc=412172%20D01%20Determining%20ERP%20and%20EIRP%20v01r01&tracking_number=47469 |title=Guidelines for Determining the Effective Radiated Power (ERP) and Equivalent Isotropically Radiated Power (EIRP) of an RF Transmitting System |accessdate=2018-08-20 |author=Federal Communications Commission Office of Engineering and Technology Laboratory Division |date=2015-08-07 |id=412172 D01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904173034/https://apps.fcc.gov/kdb/GetAttachment.html?id=fzlsGm%2Fe68Ymx58IAmzNbw%3D%3D&desc=412172%20D01%20Determining%20ERP%20and%20EIRP%20v01r01&tracking_number=47469 |archive-date=2018-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一些国家允许业余无线电操作员申请额外的临时许可<ref name="43号文件">{{Cite web|url=http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%A1%E9%83%A8%E6%97%A0201343%E5%8F%B7.pdf|title=关于实施《业余无线电台管理办法》若干事项的通知|accessdate=2017-07-07|author=中华人民共和国工业和信息化部|date=2013-02-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923132324/http://www.crac.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%A1%E9%83%A8%E6%97%A0201343%E5%8F%B7.pdf|archivedate=2017-09-23}}</ref>，以满足特定通信的要求{{noteTag|1=一些通信模式，例如卫星通信和月面反射通信，需要较大的功率以克服路径损耗。}}。

===频率使用规范和频率划分===
{{Main article|业余无线电频率划分}}
[[国际电信联盟|国际电信联盟]]（ITU）和各国政府通信部门共同管理全世界无线电频率的分配。在不对其他国家的无线电业务产生干扰的前提下，国家级通信管理部门可以在[[波段配置规划|波段配置规划]]中设立限制或者划分额外的频率给特定的无线电业务。 在一些国家，特定类型的[[无线电波发射类别表示方法|无线电发射]]在特定的频段上受到限制。在大多数国家，[[国际业余无线电联盟|国际业余无线电联盟]]（IARU）的成员协会推广频率使用规范（{{lang-en|Band plan}}）以更好地利用无线电频谱<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.iaru-r2.org/band-plan/ |title=IARU-R2 Band Plan |accessdate=2018-07-03 |author=International Amateur Radio Union – Región 2 |work=www.iaru-r2.org |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703075917/https://www.iaru-r2.org/band-plan/ |archive-date=2018-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iaru-r1.org/index.php/spectrum-and-band-plans |title=Spectrum & Band Plans |accessdate=2018-07-03 |author=International Amateur Radio Union - Region 1 |work=www.iaru-r1.org |language=en-gb |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703075706/http://www.iaru-r1.org/index.php/spectrum-and-band-plans |archivedate=2018-07-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iaru-r3.org/wp-content/files/R3-004%20Band%20Plans%20IARU%20Region%203.docx |title=Band Plans IARU Region 3 |accessdate=2018-07-03 |author=International Amateur Radio Union – Region 3 |date=2015-10-15 |id=R3-004 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216012537/http://www.iaru-r3.org/wp-content/files/R3-004%20Band%20Plans%20IARU%20Region%203.docx |archive-date=2017-12-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在少数情况下，国家通信管理机构可能允许业余无线电爱好者使用国际频率划分以外的频率<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.70mhz.org/index.php?categoryid=2&p2_articleid=316 |title=International 70 MHz allocations |accessdate=2018-08-20 |author=Bo Hansen |date=2018-06-05 |work=www.70mhz.org |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820172902/http://www.70mhz.org/index.php?categoryid=2&p2_articleid=316 |archive-date=2018-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

依照国际电信联盟的规定，在常规通信手段不可用的情况下，如果生命和财产遭受直接的威胁，无线电用户可以使用任意频率求救<ref name="RR"/>{{rp|at=4.9}}。在阿拉斯加，在灾害情况下，业余无线电爱好者可以以指定的发射类型使用阿拉斯加州紧急频率5167.5 kHz<ref name="FCC section 97.401 and 97.403">{{cite web |url=http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/search/pagedetails.action?collectionCode=CFR&searchPath=Title+47%2FChapter+I%2FSubchapter+D%2FPart+97%2FSubpart+E&granuleId=&packageId=CFR-2010-title47-vol1&oldPath=Title+47%2FChapter+I%2FSubchapter+D%2FPart+97%2FSubpart+E&fromPageDetails=true&collapse=true&ycord=536 |title=FCC Part 97 : Sec. 97.401 and 97.403 Emergency Communications |accessdate=2012-06-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128095253/https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/search/pagedetails.action?collectionCode=CFR&searchPath=Title+47%2FChapter+I%2FSubchapter+D%2FPart+97%2FSubpart+E&granuleId=&packageId=CFR-2010-title47-vol1&oldPath=Title+47%2FChapter+I%2FSubchapter+D%2FPart+97%2FSubpart+E&fromPageDetails=true&collapse=true&ycord=536 |archivedate=2016-01-28 }}</ref>。

美国的业余无线电爱好者可以申请加入{{tsl|en|Military Auxiliary Radio System|军队辅助无线电体系}}（MARS），一旦完成注册和训练，爱好者便可以在美军军用频率上为美军提供应急通信和军属口信传达服务<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mars.af.mil/Portals/59/documents/MARS%20Guide%20to%20new%20Membership%20v1.pdf |title=AFMARS New Membership Guide |accessdate=2018-01-25 |author=Air Force Military Auxiliary Radio System |date=2017-08-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126012527/http://www.mars.af.mil/Portals/59/documents/MARS%20Guide%20to%20new%20Membership%20v1.pdf |archivedate=2018-01-26 }}</ref>。
{{AmateurRadioBands|collapsed}}

==通联模式==
{{also|{{tsl|en|List of amateur radio modes|业余无线电模式列表}}}}
[[File:ICOM_IC-P7_dscn2510a.jpg|thumb]]
业余无线电爱好者使用{{tsl|en|List of amateur radio modes|业余无线电模式列表|多种模式}}进行通联。

业余无线电爱好者可以在业余波段内试验新的通联模式，但国家监管部门会要求爱好者提前公开技术细节以保证当局也能监督试验的进行<ref>{{cite wikisource |title=业余无线电台管理办法
 |year= 2012 |publisher=中华人民共和国工业和信息化部 |wslanguage= zh |quote =  业余无线电台试验新的编码、调制方式和数字通信协议等，应当事先公开并向所在地地方无线电管理机构提交相关技术信息。}}</ref>。业余无线电爱好者一般来说禁止进行加密通信，除非加密通信是用于卫星或其他设备的上行控制链路<ref>{{cite wikisource |title=业余无线电台管理办法
 |year= 2012 |publisher=中华人民共和国工业和信息化部 |wslanguage= zh |quote = 
  第二十二条 业余无线电台在通信过程中应当使用明语及业余无线电领域公认的缩略语和简语，数据文件交换应当使用公开的方式。但是，卫星业余业务中地面控制电台和空间电台之间交换的控制信号可以除外。}}</ref>。

===语音模式===
在业余无线电爱好者中最流行的两种模拟语音模式为[[频率调制|频率调制]]（FM）和[[单边带调制|单边带调制]]（SSB）。FM可以提供高音质的音频信号，而SSB适用于[[带宽|带宽]]受限的远距离通信<ref name="ARRLfaq">{{cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-faq-s |title=Ham Radio Frequently Asked Questions |work=ARRL.org |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506011537/http://www.arrl.org/ham-radio-faq-s |archivedate=2010-05-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

随着技术的进步，业余无线电爱好者和厂商也开发出了数字语音模式。数字语音模式可以提供远高于模拟模式的音质，在超短波通信中，数字语音模式大有取代FM之势，目前较为流行的有[[D-STAR|D-STAR]]，C4FM和[[数字集群通信标准|DMR]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mikemyers.me/blog/2016/2/19/d-star-dmr-fusion-which-is-right-for-you |title=D-star, DMR, Fusion, Which is right for you? |accessdate=2018-07-19 |author=Mike Myers (K3DO) |date=2016-02-19 |language=en-US |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203144412/http://www.mikemyers.me/blog/2016/2/19/d-star-dmr-fusion-which-is-right-for-you |archivedate=2018-02-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hamdigitaal.nl/?wpfb_dl=194 |title=A Comparison of Amateur RadioDigital Voice Systems |accessdate=2018-07-19 |author=Roland Kraatz, W9HPX |date=2015-07-27 |publisher=Charlotte Digital Radio Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126231831/https://www.hamdigitaal.nl/?wpfb_dl=194 |archivedate=2018-01-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===图像模式===
{{also|{{tsl|en|Amateur television|业余无线电电视}}、[[慢扫描电视|慢扫描电视]]}}

[[慢扫描电视|慢扫描电视]]（SSTV）是业余无线电爱好者的一种主要图片传输方法，慢扫描电视通过无线电传输和接收单色或彩色静态图片。慢扫描电视占用的带宽较小，因此是一种较缓慢的静态图像传输方法，通常发送一帧需要持续传输若干分钟。业余无线电操作员通常在[[短波|短波]]和[[超短波|超短波]]波段上使用慢扫描电视<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wia.org.au/members/digital/sstv/ |title=Slow Scan Television |accessdate=2018-07-18 |author=Wireless Institute of Australia |date=2018-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718114451/http://www.wia.org.au/members/digital/sstv/ |archivedate=2018-07-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

随着[[摄像头|摄像头]]等消费级的电子产品的普及，{{tsl|en|amateur television|业余无线电电视|快扫描电视}}（ATV）的普及度与日俱增，快扫描电视可以传输实时的视频画面，使得业余无线电爱好者们在通联中终于也可以告别“只闻其声，不见其人”的情况了。但因为较大的带宽占用和较高信号稳定的要求，快扫描电视通常只在{{tsl|en|70-centimeter band|70厘米波段}}（420–450 MHz）上使用，爱好者有时也在{{tsl|en|33-centimeter band|33厘米波段}}（902–928 MHz）、{{tsl|en|23-centimeter band|23厘米波段}}（1240–1300 MHz）和更高的波段上使用，这些波段[[视距传播|视距传播]]的特性将通联范围限制在30至100千米之间<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hamuniverse.com/atvfastscantv.html |title=Introduction to ATV - Amateur Radio Fast Scan TV - FSTV |accessdate=2018-07-19 |author=Bil Munsil, K1ATV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224073237/http://www.hamuniverse.com/atvfastscantv.html |archivedate=2017-12-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===无线电报===
无线电报是传统的业余无线电通信模式。[[电报|无线电报]]，也称作“CW”（等幅电报），是[[萨缪尔·摩尔斯|萨缪尔·摩尔斯]]发明的有线[[电报|电报]]技术的无线拓展，能够追溯到无线电最初的时期。尽管无线电报已被普遍认为过时<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.qd8.com.cn/shkt/shktartshow_6224.html|title=探访北京仅存的电报柜台|accessdate=2017-08-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813145446/http://www.qd8.com.cn/shkt/shktartshow_6224.html|archivedate=2017-08-13}}</ref>，但因为CW模式相较于SSB和FM的固有的抗干扰优势{{noteTag|CW模式的[[信噪比|信噪比]]高于SSB或FM模式。}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pa3fwm.nl/technotes/tn09b.html |title=Signal/noise ratio of digital amateur modes |accessdate=2017-08-14 |author=Pieter-Tjerk de Boer |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814222748/http://www.pa3fwm.nl/technotes/tn09b.html |archivedate=2017-08-14 }}</ref>，许多业余无线电爱好者们仍热衷于CW模式——特别是在[[底噪|底噪]]较大的[[短波|短波]]波段上。此外，音调更为简单的CW信号在话音无法辨认的情况下，依然能被人耳分辨出来，因此在“QRP”{{noteTag|在[[Q简语|Q简语]]中原意为“降低功率”，现引申为“低功率通信爱好者”。}}或低功率通信{{noteTag|一般认为，低功率通讯的功率范围为5 W及以下，可以在呼号添加/QRP后缀，当发射功率不超过1 W时，可在呼号添加/QRPp后缀。意为“极低功率发射”。}}爱好者中广受青睐<ref name="QRP">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arrl.org/why-qrp |title=Why QRP? |accessdate=2017-08-14 |author=Kenny A. Chaffin |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815025008/http://www.arrl.org/why-qrp |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>。纯CW发信机结构较为简单，易于制作，使得CW模式也在{{tsl|en|Amateur radio homebrew|自制（业余无线电）|电子制作爱好者}}中也占有一席之地。<ref name="QRP"/>CW通联中，爱好者们常常使用[[Q简语|Q简语]]和其他通信简略语，这使得CW成为了跨越语言和口音鸿沟的交流桥梁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.morsecodeclassnet.com/lesson5/ |title=Amateur radio Q Signals ~ Lesson 5 |accessdate=2018-06-08 |author=www.MorseCodeClassNet.com |date=2016-02-03 |quote=Amateur operators break down cultural and language barriers through communication while using standardized shorthand. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608083550/http://www.morsecodeclassnet.com/lesson5/ |archivedate=2018-06-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.electronics-notes.com/articles/ham_radio/morse_code/what-is-the-morse-code.php |title=What is Morse Code? What is CW? |accessdate=2018-06-08 |author=Electronics Notes |work=www.electronics-notes.com |quote=Using the standard abbreviations basic contacts can be conducted with a limited knowledge of the language of the other person. |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613034735/https://www.electronics-notes.com/articles/ham_radio/morse_code/what-is-the-morse-code.php |archivedate=2017-06-13 }}</ref>。专业的报务技术和能力许多年来一直是取得使用30 MHz以下频率的业余无线电执照的条件，但随着2003年国际条例的修改，许多国家不再要求爱好者掌握报务技术<ref name="fcc06-178a1">{{cite web |url=http://hraunfoss.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/FCC-06-178A1.pdf |format=PDF |title=FCC Report and Order 06-178A1 |publisher=[[联邦通信委员会|Federal Communications Commission]] |page=7 |date=2006-12-19 |accessdate=2007-05-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019174829/http://hraunfoss.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/FCC-06-178A1.pdf |archivedate=2011-10-19 }}</ref>。在[[美国|美国]]，[[联邦通信委员会|联邦通信委员会]]于2003年2月23日取消了所有执照等级的报务技术要求<ref name="e7-729">{{cite journal |url=http://edocket.access.gpo.gov/2007/pdf/E7-729.pdf |format=PDF |title=47 CFR Part 97 |author=Federal Communications Commission |journal=Federal Register |publisher=Government Printing Office |location=[[Washington,_D.C.|Washington, D.C.]] |volume=72 |issue=15 |pages=3081–3082 |date=2007-01-24 |accessdate=2007-12-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080216095957/http://edocket.access.gpo.gov/2007/pdf/E7-729.pdf |archivedate=2008-02-16 }}</ref><ref name="morsedropped1">{{cite web |url=http://www.unwiredadventures.com/unwire/2006/12/fcc_to_drop_mor.html |title=FCC to Drop Morse Testing for ''All'' Amateur License Classes |work=ARRL.org ''via'' UnwiredAdventures.com |date=2006-12-15 |accessdate=2010-05-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090927165317/http://www.unwiredadventures.com/unwire/2006/12/fcc_to_drop_mor.html |archivedate=2009-09-27 }}</ref>。

===数字模式===
[[File:一种单工mmdvm盒子的内部结构.jpg|thumb]]
[[数码|数字]]模式利用[[编码|编码]]和[[信号处理|信号处理]]技术，将语音、文字、图像和数据等信息编码成[[数字信号|数字信号]]后发送，拥有相较于[[模拟|模拟]]制式更强的抗干扰能力<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tapr.org/pdf/DCC2011-IntroDigitalDataModes-N2ABP.pdf |title=Introduction to DIGITAL DATA MODES |accessdate=2018-08-20 |author=George Heron |date=2011-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113120736/http://tapr.org/pdf/DCC2011-IntroDigitalDataModes-N2ABP.pdf |archive-date=2012-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大多数业余无线电数据模式使用[[频移键控|频移键控]]（FSK）、[[相移键控|相移键控]]（PSK）和[[幅移键控|幅移键控]]（ASK）技术，将编码后的数字信号转换为模拟语音信号后再由电台发送，使用[[单边带调制|单边带调制]]（SSB）的调制模式<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/908700871 |title=The ARRL General Class License Manual |last=Ward |first=Silver, H. |publisher=American Radio Relay League |year=2015 |isbn=9781625950307 |edition=8th edition |location=Newington, CT |page=6-9 |oclc=908700871 |quote=Most digital modes on HF are transmitted as LSB signal except for JT65 and JT9 which use USB. |access-date=2018-08-20 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829121832/https://www.worldcat.org/title/arrl-general-class-license-manual-for-ham-radio-all-you-need-to-pass-your-general-class-exam/oclc/908700871 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[个人计算机|个人计算机]]的普及促进了各种[[数码|数字]]模式的使用，许多数字模式曾经需要[[调制解调器|调制解调器]]和笨重的设备，但现在可以利用个人计算机和软件编解码。例如{{tsl|en|radioteletype|无线电传}}（RTTY），之前需要笨重的电传打字机，而现在利用一台电脑就可以实现通联了<ref name="Missouri">{{cite web |url=http://www.kh6bb.org/photos1.html |title=KH6BB USS Missouri Radio Room Photos |work=KH6BB USS Missouri Battleship Radio Room, kh6bb.org |accessdate=2010-05-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101216035321/http://www.kh6bb.org/photos1.html |archivedate=2010-12-16 }}</ref>。

业余无线电爱好者为不同用途开发了不同的数字模式。火腿族引领了1970年代[[封包无线电|封包无线电]]的开发，并吸收了许多其他协议的细节，例如{{tsl|en|AX.25|AX.25}}和[[TCP/IP协议族|TCP/IP]]，实现了通过业余无线电发送数据包的功能<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hflink.com/alehamradio/ |title=ALE in Ham Radio |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=Bonnie Crystal |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707013541/http://hflink.com/alehamradio/ |archivedate=2017-07-07 }}</ref>。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tapr.org/pr_intro.html |title=Packet Radio: Introduction to Packet Radio |accessdate=2017-08-15 |author=Greg Jones |date=1995 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815103103/https://www.tapr.org/pr_intro.html |archivedate=2017-08-15 }}</ref>利用{{tsl|en|PSK31|PSK31}}和{{tsl|en|Olivia MFSK|Olivia MFSK}}等模式，爱好者们能够在强干扰的情况下进行实时的文字交流。自动链路建立（ALE）技术能够使业余无线电网络持续性地在具有全球覆盖的[[短波|短波]]波段上运行。FT8和JT65等数字模式使用例如{{tsl|en|WSJT (Amateur radio software)|WSJT（业余无线电软件）|WSTJ}}的专用软件进行编解码，这些模式具有极强的抗干扰和纠错能力，但只能交换必要的信息，无法用于聊天，通常只用于[[流星余迹通信|流星余迹通信]]、月面反射通信和其他极端干扰环境下的通联<ref name="WJST"></ref>。

